## Tag

### Prop \`visible\` removed. Use conditional rendering instead.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

Replace \`visible\` prop with conditional rendering using \`{condition && <Tag>...</Tag>}\`.

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
<Tag visible={show}>Tag</Tag>
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
{show && <Tag>Tag</Tag>}
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`<Tag[^>]*\\bvisible\\b\`

